# proping v1.0 [ping from dst]

Description :
We need to checking server's status sometimes, for example we power on server and we will checking server status [up or down]. this problem solved by 'proping' program. just run program like this : proping 192.168.1.1
when server uped, program print message in terminal and show notification on your desktop.

Dependencies:
	1. ping
	2. echo
	3. sleep
	4. sox

Install proping v1.0:
	1. sudo ./install.sh -i

Uninstall proping v1.0:
	1. sudo rm -f /usr/bin/proping

Usage proping v1.0:
	1. proping [IP Address]
